formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. Estimated cost of construction as per Engineer's certificate is inclusive of all the expenses i.e. Construction and onsite expenses.
2. Partner's representation is relied upon for estimated Finance Cost and Statutory Expenses.
3. Reliance has been laid on the Partner's representation for carpet area of the units sold/unsold as required in the Annexure to the certificate.
4. Reliance has been laid on the Partner's representation for estimated cost of the project.
5. Land is valued at cost and no inflation is provided.
6. The figures and values are based on unaudited books presented before us till 22.07.2022
7. Flat B-701 is UAE national and country code+97 has been removed from the mobile number. FLAT A 1302 is a US resident. Country Code +01 has been removed in Annexure 3A
8. amount withdrawn from rera account is inclusive of bank charges
9. The secured loans is CC facility availed from the bank. Hence the actual utilization may vary than disbursed amount. Hence outstanding amount is disclosed.
10. The entire o/s. including GST has been treated as unpaid and deducted from expenditure.
11. The balances of unsecured loan are subject to confirmation.
